CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

November 25, 2013

[Cite as 11/25/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-Ohio-5173.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-1543. Sullins v. Raycom Media, Inc.

Cuyahoga App. No. 99235, 2013-Ohio-3530. This cause is pending before the court as a jurisdictional appeal.

Upon consideration of appellant WUAB and WOIO, L.L.C.’s motion to strike the second memorandum in response to jurisdiction filed by appellee Lavelle Sullins, it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
